{"tid":439141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國務院網站撤中華民國國旗 台灣多次向美國溝通無效","createTime":"2017-10-17T14:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T00:41:30.000Z","uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f14dc11d8eb0ddaa12c1567cc3063242dd0e3cdc","tid":439141,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:12:25.000Z","msg":"美國務院網站撤我國旗　溝通無效<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=640&amp;q=70&amp;src=https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/59e59dad4d181a6feff0c3c0_201710171405.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D640%26q%3D70%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F59e59dad4d181a6feff0c3c0_201710171405.jpg&h=c2892470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國川普總統上任後，美國國務院網站改版，將中華民國國旗從「與美國交往的國家」網頁中拿掉。<span style=\"color: red;\">外交部17日表示，政府已經多次向美國溝通，強烈要求掛回中華民國國旗，但美國立場堅定，只表示對我方的政策沒有任何改變。</span><br />\n<br />\n外交部北美司長陳立國表示，政府已經多次向美方表達要「掛回我方國旗」的立場，但美方都只回應，他們對台灣的政策沒有任何改變。我方於是向美方表達，希望這樣的情形不要再度發生，也避免引發外界不必要的聯想。外交部表示，美方對於我方的的訴求，已經明確了解。<br />\n<br />\n媒體詢問，美方是否願意掛回中華民國的國旗？陳立國表示，美方的回應仍是，「他們對台灣的政策沒有任何改變」。<br />\n<br />\n陳立國指出，台美關係緊密，雙方的溝通非常順暢，政府希望美方繼續維持一貫的立場，不希望有任何突兀的改變。但美方的回覆都是相同，我方當然無法滿意，仍強烈希望掛回我國國旗，但美方對於我方的答覆，依舊沒有改變。<br />\n<br />\n這次美國國務院網站拿掉我國國旗，外界解讀可能是中國大陸為了壓制台獨聲浪，對美國施壓。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.nownews.com/news/2626402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F2626402&d=gyZJa1c7dB5TSZsP%2FLFtkP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4662fa44\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.nownews.com/news/2626402</a>"},{"pid":"0073a8b8f656ab6d237c64011b2e8c0be581f303","tid":439141,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:13:44.000Z","msg":"侵侵話遵守美國&quot;一個中國政策&quot;"},{"pid":"b6d69f8ab739d489edd6d9dfaac909a333f0eb2f","tid":439141,"uid":33477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>侵侵話遵守美國&quot;一個中國政策&quot;</blockquote><br />\n一中一台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yovms8cj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyovms8cj&h=26926bc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5490748792c4044a6b197b2db016343078a25b26","tid":439141,"uid":93986,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:18:14.000Z","msg":"冇力量既國家就是垃圾<br />\n千古不變"},{"pid":"cc955ca6c5af101f22220f3d224a947d8777388c","tid":439141,"uid":114692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:18:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14b53052bef2bf79288a24c7019b3e3d6c1c1bb9","tid":439141,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>侵侵話遵守美國&quot;一個中國政策&quot;</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://image.peoplenews.tw/collection/1480933097.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.peoplenews.tw%2Fcollection%2F1480933097.png&h=8d1fe42c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1dfe8b2c3b41e354528d0f587e097c310a1c5f6","tid":439141,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img5.cna.com.tw/www/webphotos/500/20170930/47868967.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2Fwebphotos%2F500%2F20170930%2F47868967.jpg&h=86399f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有ROC國旗即係中國領土<br />\n無任何國旗即係主權未定"},{"pid":"508a6bdc138eecc323dc0a4ab3ae70ed645afc18","tid":439141,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e940eacb2a1e98612308da8ad41c4b146f1c14e2","tid":439141,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"